1️⃣ Tell me about yourself

Usually the first question.

They check:

Communication

Experience summary

Confidence

Tip: Keep it 1–2 minutes.

2️⃣ Tell me about a challenging problem you solved

They want to understand:

Problem-solving ability

Technical thinking

Example you can use:

Razorpay payment integration

Debugging a production issue

Fixing a performance problem

3️⃣ Tell me about a time you made a mistake

This checks:

Accountability

Learning mindset

Safe approach:

Explain the mistake → how you fixed it → what you learned.

4️⃣ Tell me about a time you received critical feedback

They want to see if you are open to feedback.

Example:

Code review suggestion

Performance improvement suggestion

5️⃣ Tell me about a conflict with a teammate

They check:

Professional behavior

Communication skills

Best approach:

Explain how you discussed and resolved the issue respectfully.

6️⃣ Tell me about a time you handled a tight deadline

They want to know if you can work under pressure.

Mention:

Prioritizing tasks

Coordinating with team

Delivering the feature

7️⃣ Tell me about a time you improved an existing system

This shows initiative.

Examples:

Optimizing database queries

Reducing API response time

Refactoring messy code

8️⃣ Tell me about a time you helped a teammate

They check team collaboration.

Example:

Helping debug an issue

Explaining a solution

Reviewing code

9️⃣ Tell me about a time you had to learn something quickly

This shows adaptability.

Example:

Learning a new gem

Learning a new tool

Understanding a new business domain

🔟 Tell me about a production issue you handled

Managers love this question.

Explain:

What happened

How you debugged

How you fixed it

How you prevented it again

⭐ Tip for answering behavioral questions

Use the STAR method:

S → Situation

T → Task

A → Action

R → Result

Example:

Situation: We had a performance issue in one API
Task: I needed to identify the cause
Action: I analyzed logs and found an N+1 query
Result: After fixing it with eager loading, response time improved significantly

